ConcurrentSkipListDictionary<TKey,TValue> is a C# port of Doug Lea's
java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentSkipListMap (the CAS-based, lock-free skip
list algorithm). That original work was written by Doug Lea with assistance
from members of JCP JSR-166 and released to the public domain, as explained
at http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

This port adapts the algorithm to the CLR (fully generic, no boxing of keys
or values) but the design and correctness arguments are Lea's. The port and
all other code in this repository are licensed under the MIT License.
